.
起飞之前，机长在舱门口展开了一面五星红旗。
Before taking off, the captain unfurled a five-star red flag at the hatch.
这趟航班虽然只有9名乘客，但满载的是中国人民的战“疫”祝福与支持。
Although this flight only 9 passengers, but full of the Chinese people's war "plague" blessing and support.
9名飞往意大利的“逆行者”，是真正的国际主义战士。
The nine "Inverters" who flew to Italy were true internationalists.
文|阿　晖新冠肺炎疫情在全球暴发，目前确诊病例已经破万的意大利形势极为严峻，几乎就是欧洲的“湖北”。
With the global outbreak of new crown pneumonia, Italy, which has now seen 10, 000 confirmed cases, is in dire condition, almost Europe's "Hubei."
在医疗物资和设备短缺的困难之下，意大利外长迪马约3月10日在与国务委员兼外长王毅通电话时，向中国提出了紧急求助。
Faced with a shortage of medical supplies and equipment, Italian Foreign Minister Di Maiyo sent an urgent call to China on March 10 during a telephone conversation with State Councilor and Foreign Minister Wang Yi.
向遭受疫情影响的国家提供国际合作与支援，是中国的一贯态度。
It is China's consistent attitude to provide international cooperation and support to countries affected by the epidemic.
疫情紧急，说做就做。
The epidemic is urgent. Do what you say.
仅仅两天之后，一支由9名中国医疗专家组成的援意“志愿军”就踏上了飞往意大利的征程。
Just two days later, a volunteer corps of nine Chinese medical experts set out on a flight to Italy.
昨天（3月12日）17:30，一架东航A350-900客机从上海浦东机场起飞，执行MU787包机航班，将中国政府和中国红十字会向意大利派遣的抗疫专家组一行9人与约9吨物资，从上海运往罗马。
At 17: 30 yesterday (March 12), an East China Airlines A350-900 took off from Shanghai's Pudong airport on a chartered flight MU787, transporting a team of nine people and about nine tons of supplies from Shanghai to Rome from the Chinese Government and the Chinese Red Cross to Italy.
两千岁的丝绸之路，开启了守望相助的战“疫”新篇。
The 2,000-year-old Silk Road opened a new chapter in the battle against SARS.
据悉，这是东航引进A350新机型以来，用该机型承运人数最少的一班航班。
It is reported that this is China Eastern Airlines introduced a new A350 aircraft, with the aircraft carrying the least number of flights.
而在这架援意航班顺利起飞的背后，一些细节令人感动。
Behind the successful take-off of the aid flight, some details were touching.
3小时完成航班批复3月11日晚上9时许，一条紧急运输中国赴意大利专家组和防疫物资包机的任务指令，从民航局发送到了东航。
3 hours to complete flight clearance March 11 around 9 p.m., an emergency shipment of Chinese experts to Italy and epidemic prevention air charter mission instructions, from the Civil Aviation Authority sent to China Eastern.
疫情以来已经执行了多次国内外抗疫包机任务的东航，立即启动响应，连夜召开准备会行动起来。
Since the outbreak has carried out a number of domestic and international anti-epidemic charter missions, immediately launched a response, even the convening of the preparatory meeting overnight into action.
“目前，中意航线已经临时停运，所以包机必须取得当地起落批复。
"At present, the routes between China and Italy have been temporarily suspended, so charter flights have to get local clearance.
”东航国防动员办公室副主任彭海彦说。
Peng Haiyan, deputy director of China Eastern's defence mobilization office, said.
经过东航总部的运行控制等部门与罗马当地营业部密切配合，最终在北京时间12日凌晨零点刚过，就获得了意大利方面的包机批复。
After the operation of the headquarters of China Eastern and other departments and Rome's local business department, and finally in the Beijing time just after 0 a.m. on the Italian side of the charter approval.
我国派往意大利的专家组成员一行9人，来自国家卫健委、中国红十字会、中国疾控中心、四川省红十字会、四川省疾病预防控制中心、四川大学华西医院等单位，都已经在国内战“疫”前沿连续奋战，有着新冠肺炎疫情防控和治疗的丰富经验，有的专家还经历过汶川抗震、援助西非埃博拉疫区等诸多重大考验。
Our team of experts sent to Italy is composed of nine members from the National Fitness and Health Commission, the Chinese Red Cross, the China CDC, the Sichuan Red Cross, the Sichuan Center for Disease Control and Prevention, and the Sichuan University's Huaxi Hospital.
考虑到医疗物资体积大、不耐压，虽然专家组一行仅为9人，A330宽体机即可承运，但为了让发往意大利的防疫物资能顺畅安全运输。
Given the size and unbearable pressure of medical supplies, the A330 wide-bodied aircraft can be carried by the Group's team of only nine people, but in order to allow for the smooth and safe transport of epidemic prevention supplies destined for Italy.
东航研究决定，派出腹舱容量更大、机龄不到1年的最新锐A350-900机型，执行这一航班。
China Eastern decided to send its newest sharp A350-900 aircraft with a larger belly capacity and less than a year old to carry out the flight.
3名资深机长与自制辣酱“护航”从上海到罗马，空中航程9619公里，需要飞行12小时。
The three senior captains travelled 9,619 kilometers by air from Shanghai to Rome in a homemade "escort" of 12 hours.
为保障此次航班，东航上海飞行部在高手云集的A350飞行团队中，精心挑选了3名经验丰富、技术出色的党员机长执行航班。
To secure the flight, China Eastern's Shanghai Flight Department carefully selected three experienced and skilled party leaders to fly on the highly skilled A350 flight team.
其中带队的林波机长总飞行时间17000小时，是A320、A350机型教员，黄维和杨建峰两名机长飞行时间分别为20000和18000小时；郎春力、唐伟彬、贾正宇3名90后副驾驶也都是东航飞行部“A350墨镜侠战疫青年突击队”的成员，飞行时间在1600-2800小时，他们早在2月1日就已经提交了请战书，请缨一旦有特殊任务时冲锋在前。
Captain Lin Po, who led the crew, flew 17,000 hours, a total of 20,000 and 18,000 hours for A320 and A350, respectively. The two pilots, Lang Chunli, Tang Weibin and Jia Zhengyu, were also members of the Eastern Airlines Flight Department's "A350 Shaoxidian Youth Commando Team," flying between 1600 and 2800 hours.
东航同样选派了优秀的客舱团队保障航班。
China Eastern also has excellent cabin crew to guarantee flights.
其中，客舱经理郑挺欣曾执飞过我国维和部队运输包机、赴泰国撤运中方人员包机、运送大兴安岭火灾消防官兵包机等诸多特殊航班。
Among them, cabin manager Zheng Jia Xin has flown over China's peacekeeping forces chartered aircraft, to Thailand to evacuate Chinese personnel chartered aircraft, transport Daxing An Ling fire-fighting officers and soldiers charter flights and many other special flights.
在航前准备会上，乘务组成员亲手写下了祝福卡片，向远行的专家们传递问候，也一一敲定服务细节：因为这次是包机，所以旅客不能像商业航班一样申请wifi账号，乘务员们就决定把自己的账号拿出来，方便专家们上网和给家人报平安；大家还商定，要把个人多出的消毒液、洗手液留给专家组，让他们在意大利的物资供应更充裕。
In the run-up to the flight, crew members hand-written greeting cards, sent greetings to the travelling experts and finalized the service details: as this was a chartered flight, passengers could not apply for a wifi account like a commercial flight, and it was agreed to leave the excess disinfectant and hand sanitizer to the expert group for better supplies in Italy.
让医疗组专家没想到的是，登上飞机后居然还收到了一份特殊的礼物——东航食品专门制作的辣酱。
To the surprise of the medical experts, they received a special gift after boarding the plane.
东航地服部也专门准备了一批方便面等食材，配上航班。
East Airways Department also prepared a number of special instant noodles and other food materials, with flights.
这一切，都是考虑到专家组一行在意大利的生活后勤所需，让他们能更好地执行援助任务。
All of this was in view of the logistical requirements of the Group's life in Italy, which would allow them to better carry out their assistance tasks.
3度申请起飞时间这架包机的专家从北京、上海、成都多地汇聚而来，物资更是来自多个省市，由于疫情期间意大利方面的相关规定，专家组还得在国内医院完成检测、开具健康证明，环节可谓千头万绪。
Experts from Beijing, Shanghai and Chengdu are among the experts on the chartered flight, which comes from many provinces and cities, and the team has had to complete tests and issue health certificates in hospitals around the country due to Italian regulations during the outbreak.
“物资什么时候到齐，进上海了没有？”“我们在等候物资和专家组健康证明，请再次申请航班时刻”……3月12日中午，彭海彦一边努力往嘴里塞着午饭，一边连着接打了十多个电话，几乎随时都在“一嘴二用”。
"When did the supplies arrive in Shanghai?" "We are waiting for the supplies and the expert group's health certificate, please apply for flight time again..." At noon on March 12, Peng Hai-yan made more than a dozen consecutive phone calls while trying to cram his lunch into his mouth.
像彭海彦一样，每个保障这趟航班的东航人都异常忙碌。
Like Mr Peng, everyone who guarantees this flight is very busy.
东航原定为MU787包机申请的浦东机场出港时刻为3月12日12:30，但因为物资运输原因，此后又向管制部门一再申请变更，申请15:00、申请17:00……终于， 8.6吨腹舱物资和300多公斤托运行李都装载完毕，赶上了第3个节点。
The departure time of Pudong Airport, originally requested by China Eastern for charter flight MU787, was 12: 30 March. However, due to material transportation reasons, China Eastern repeatedly applied to the regulatory authorities for a change, requesting 15: 00 and 17: 00.
包机从浦东机场腾空而起。
The chartered plane soared from Pudong Airport.
起飞之前，机长在舱门口展开了一面五星红旗。
Before taking off, the captain unfurled a five-star red flag at the hatch.
这趟航班虽然只有9名乘客，但满载的是中国人民的战“疫”祝福与支持。
Although this flight only 9 passengers, but full of the Chinese people's war "plague" blessing and support.
9名飞往意大利的“逆行者”，是真正的国际主义战士。
The nine "Inverters" who flew to Italy were true internationalists.
万米高空，机长广播在客舱萦绕：“尊敬的白衣战士：很荣幸今天能陪你们一起奔赴意大利抗疫前线。
"Distinguished White Soldier: It is a great honor to accompany you today to the front of the Italian epidemic.
中国的杏林即将满园，春日的阳光洒满心间，在你们的护佑下，家乡的人民安全了，但你们却不能脱下战袍，还要继续无畏地逆行，用医者的仁心厚德去守护更多的人民。
The Chinese almond groves will soon be full of gardens, the spring sunshine will fill the heart, and under your protection, the people of your hometown will be safe, but you will not be able to take off your robes, but will continue to tread fearlessly backward, guarding more people with the kindness and kindness of the healer.
命运与共，爱无国界，我们深信，全人类守望相助，终将战胜病魔！最后，我谨代表机组和全体东航人向你们致以最高的敬意！我们等你们捷报，接你们回家！”征集令阳春三月，万物复苏。
In conclusion, on behalf of the crew and all the Eastern Airways, I would like to pay the highest respects to you! We are waiting for your prompt report to take you home!
在抗击疫情的战斗中，我们迎来了春天，《新民周刊》也迎来了新闻线索和故事征集的第二弹。
In the fight against the epidemic, we ushered in the spring, "New People's Weekly" also ushered in the news clues and the second round of story collection.
如今，经历了一个多月休眠的城市正在逐渐苏醒，各行各业都开始有序复工复产。
Now, after more than a month of dormancy of the city is gradually waking up, all walks of life began to orderly resumption of work.
不论您是企业老板、管理者，还是普通员工；又或者，您是老师、家长，还是学生本人……我们希望了解复工复产复学过程中的困难，或暖心故事。
Whether you're a business owner, a manager, or an employee, or whether you're a teacher, parent, or student... we'd like to know about the difficulties of getting back to work, or a warm heart story.
如果你是抗疫一线的医生护士，疫情期间拍下了珍贵的摄影作品，也欢迎联系我们投稿。
If you are a first-line doctor and nurse against the epidemic, you have taken valuable photographs during the epidemic and are welcome to contact us for contributions.
当然，抗击新冠肺炎疫情的相关故事，我们仍然欢迎。
Of course, the story of fighting the outbreak of New Crown Pneumonia is still welcome.
希望广大读者朋友，提供相关线索，说出你的故事，让我们用新闻留存这一切。
I hope that the general reader friends, provide relevant clues, tell your story, let us use the news to retain all this.
